    "has_raw_measurements": true,
    "raw_measurement_details": "Raw biological measurements include PacBio SMRT long reads from H. erectus genomic DNA, Illumina paired-end reads from 358 resequenced seahorse specimens, Hi-C sequencing reads for chromosome scaffolding, and embryo imaging data from whole-mount in situ hybridization. The paper also mentions genotype information extracted from BAM files for PSMC and sequence data used for SNP calling, phylogenetics, and selection analyses.",
    "dataset_characterization": {
      "data_availability_statement": "The paper repeatedly states that source data are provided in a Source Data file and that multiple analysis outputs are deposited at Figshare as Datasets 1–9. Specific examples include DNA sequences and estimated phylogenetic tree (Dataset 1), nucleotide diversity (Dataset 2), ortholog alignments and gene trees (Dataset 3), ASTRAL inference (Dataset 4), BEAST input/output files (Dataset 5), geographic diversification outputs (Dataset 6), PSMC demographic histories (Dataset 7), dN/dS results for candidate genes (Dataset 8), and protein trees for 37 PSGs (Dataset 9).",
      "data_provided_types": [
        "raw",
